-On the slope.

976
01:22:14,999 --> 01:22:17,559
-On the slope-- Ah. Hagrid.
-Professor Dumbledore.

977
01:22:17,719 --> 01:22:20,313
-Good evening.
-Minister. Make your way through.

978
01:22:20,519 --> 01:22:24,194
-Have a tea. if you like.
-No. Hagrid.

979
01:22:26,199 --> 01:22:28,667
-Gent|emen.
-|'d like a cup of tea.

980
01:22:28,880 --> 01:22:32,077
