984
01:22:45,440 --> 01:22:48,830
-Dear. dear....
-Now. now. Hagrid. Now. come on.

985
01:22:49,039 --> 01:22:53,237
-All right. It'll be all right.
-The execution shall dispatch--

986
01:22:53,399 --> 01:22:55,071
What?

987
01:22:55,239 --> 01:22:57,230
I thought I just saw--

988
01:22:57,400 --> 01:22:59,436
-Never mind.
-Let's go!

989
01:23:04,319 --> 01:23:06,549
Buckbeak didn't mean no harm.

990
01:23:51,160 --> 01:23:52,559
Oh. no.

991
01:24:03,039 --> 01:24:05,155
He bit me. Scabbers.

992
01:24:05,720 --> 01:24:07,597
Ron. Ron!

993
01:24:08,520 --> 01:24:11,910
-Ron!
-Scabbers. come back.

994
01:24:13,359 --> 01:24:15,031
Wait!

995
01:24:20,720 --> 01:24:24,838
-Scabbers. you bit me!
-Harry. you do realize what tree this is?

996
01:24:25,000 --> 01:24:27,195
That's not good. Ron. run!

997
01:24:30,199 --> 01:24:32,633
Harry. Hermione. run!

998
01:24:33,199 --> 01:24:34,757
It's the Grim!

999
01:24:41,479 --> 01:24:44,391
-Harry!
-Ron! Ron. wait!

1000
01:24:44,599 --> 01:24:46,510
Harry!

1001
01:24:48,039 --> 01:24:50,314
-He|p!
-Ron!

1002
01:24:52,359 --> 01:24:55,476
-Ron. Ron.
-Ron!

1003
01:25:09,720 --> 01:25:11,631
Come on!

1004
01:25:13,479 --> 01:25:14,832
Move!

1005
01:25:18,720 --> 01:25:20,392
Duck!

1006
01:25:54,799 --> 01:25:56,994
Harry!

1007
01:26:12,239 --> 01:26:15,117
-Oh. I'm sorry.
-Don't worry.

1008
01:26:15,280 --> 01:26:19,034
-Where do you suppose this goes?
-I have a hunch.

1009
01:26:19,559 --> 01:26:20,992
ljust hope I'm wrong.

1010
01:26:39,880 --> 01:26:42,917
We're in the Shrieking Shack.
aren't we?

1011
01:26:43,960 --> 01:26:45,518
Come on.

1012
01:26:55,439 --> 01:26:56,792
Ron.

1013
01:26:57,319 --> 01:26:59,833
-Ron. You're okay.
-The dog. Where is it?

1014
01:27:00,039 --> 01:27:03,111
It's a trap. He's the dog.
He's an Animagus.

1015
01:27:16,439 --> 01:27:19,112
If you want to kill Harry.
you have to kill us too!

1016
01:27:19,280 --> 01:27:20,998
No. Only one will die tonight.

1017
01:27:21,199 --> 01:27:23,030
Then it'll be you!

1018
01:27:28,999 --> 01:27:31,069
Are you going to kill me. Harry?

1019
01:27:32,239 --> 01:27:33,991
