1020
01:27:37,559 --> 01:27:41,552
Well. well. Sirius.
Looking rather ragged. aren't we?

1021
01:27:41,760 --> 01:27:44,672
Finally. the flesh
reflects the madness within.

1022
01:27:45,239 --> 01:27:48,709
Well. you'd know all about
the madness within. wouldn't you?

1023
01:27:58,720 --> 01:27:59,709
-I found him.
-I know.

1024
01:27:59,880 --> 01:28:01,108
